Project starts 2026-05-16

' Phases
[단기 (3개월)] lasts 90 days
[단기 (3개월)] is colored in #C8E6C9

[중기 (6~12개월)] lasts 180 days
[중기 (6~12개월)] starts 90 days after [단기 (3개월)]'s start
[중기 (6~12개월)] is colored in #FFF9C4

[장기 (1~2년)] lasts 365 days
[장기 (1~2년)] starts 180 days after [중기 (6~12개월)]'s start
[장기 (1~2년)] is colored in #FFE0B2

